data: {"candidates": [{"content": {"parts": [{"text": "**Considering Joke Options**\n\nI've decided to go with a classic, family-friendly joke, a simple one-liner to be precise. I've considered a few options, and one I think is promising is: \"Why don't scientists trust atoms? Because they make up everything!\"\n\n\n","thought": true}],"role": "model"},"index": 0}],"usageMetadata": {"promptTokenCount": 7,"totalTokenCount": 72,"promptTokensDetails": [{"modality": "TEXT","tokenCount": 7}],"thoughtsTokenCount": 65,"serviceTier": "standard"},"modelVersion": "gemini-2.5-flash","responseId": "puz_adKXKfC1_uMPvd7WuAU"}

data: {"candidates": [{"content": {"parts": [{"text": "**Selecting The Atoms Joke**\n\nI've settled on the \"atoms\" joke; its conciseness and widespread recognition make it ideal. While the \"impasta\" and \"scarecrow\" puns were strong contenders, I felt the atoms joke hit the mark the best for a family-friendly, one-liner.\n\n\n","thought": true}],"role": "model"},"index": 0}],"usageMetadata": {"promptTokenCount": 7,"totalTokenCount": 219,"promptTokensDetails": [{"modality": "TEXT","tokenCount": 7}],"thoughtsTokenCount": 212,"serviceTier": "standard"},"modelVersion": "gemini-2.5-flash","responseId": "puz_adKXKfC1_uMPvd7WuAU"}

